14. DISASTER AFTERMATH: WHAT TO EXPECT IN THE LONGER TERM 
    by Ed Perkins

By now, you've heard the TV pundits' orotund pronouncements and read
the purple prose: Following the disasters of September 11, air travel
in the U.S. will permanently change. And they're probably right.

For the full story, please visit
http://rd.SmarterLiving.com/da100401.14
<A HREF="rd.SmarterLiving.com/da100401.14">AOL</A>

